
** Commands

Added additional the publishing command to $LOCAL/Makefile
*publish-wiki*.  Publishing inside a wiki mode with table.el made
problems to due of table.el. To edit a table you have to *load* now
explicitly the table.el package.

+-----+-----+
|1    |2    |  
+-----+-----+
|3    |4    |
+-----+-----+

** Syntax

<example>
The usage of the string "\|" in a normal wiki sentence makes
problems. Usage in the context of a example struct - as here
demonstrated - works.
</example>
